#bienvenue=&Welcome to ^1
#bienvenue0=&Welcome to Engarde 10

#bienvenue11=&Because of a change in contexts, versions 10.1 and later are not compatible with earlier versions.
#bienvenue12=&For more information, see "Help | Recent Manuals xx | versions".
#bienvenue13=&With Engarde Smart the referees or the piste assistants can enter the results of the matches on the piste.

#bienvenue14=&It is not recommended to open "by files" the competitions in auxiliary and with DiapoEngarde. It can produce read/write conflicts in files.
#bienvenue15=&It is better to use the client-server mode (competitions shown in a green banner) or DiapoEngarde by internet.

#bienvenue16=&Version 10.2 includes the evolutions made for the World Championships in Budapest 2019 and the evolutions of August 2019.
#bienvenue17=&The list of these evolutions can be found on the engarde-escrime.com website in the version history.

