#pas_abandon4=&If the opposing competitor has N points and the abandoning competitor has P points and N<=P, 
#pas_abandon5=&give P points to the competitor who abandons and P+1 points to the opposite competitor.

#expli_forfait1=&In "Match-by-match forfeits" mode,  type f as score for a forfeit
